  <title>Third-level Administrative Divisions, Vietnam, 2015</title>
  <abstract>This polygon shapefile contains the third-level administrative divisions of Vietnam (adm3). Level 3 divisions include communes, rural communes, and wards. This layer is part of the Global Administrative Areas 2015 (v2.8) dataset.
